===PC Game The Sims===
PC Game The Sims (Created by EA and Maxis)

Create and play in Virtual worlds.
Control virtually every aspect of Your Sims' lives, in the PC game of all time! Make them charming or churlish, timid or tempestuous. Place them in the lap of luxury or an armpit of a hovel. Their lives are in your hands.

